OL,3,CEx-employee helped himself to #52,000
OL,4,Cworth of fuel on company account
OL,6,FAn ex-employee used company fuel cards
OL,7,Fto buy #52,000 of fuel he was not
OL,8,Fentitled to.
OL,10,FPhilip James, 25, went on a three-
OL,11,Fmonth fuel spree at truck stops and
OL,12,Fgarages across the North West using
OL,13,Fcards he should have given back,
OL,14,Ffilling barrels and tanks using false
OL,15,Fregistration plates to avoid detection.
OL,17,FBy the time he was caught he had made
OL,18,Fmore than 120 purchases totalling
OL,19,F33,470 of fuel.
