OL,3,CEx-employee helped himself to #52,000
OL,4,Cworth of fuel on company account
OL,6,FCCTV showed him filling up at
OL,7,FEurogarages Rivington, on the M61, and
OL,8,Fon some occasions he bought more than
OL,9,F#500 worth of fuel in a single
OL,10,Ftransaction.
OL,12,FInvestigators seized footage and
OL,13,Freceipts which showed James was
OL,14,Fresponsible for the bogus purchases.
OL,16,FIn May 2019, James began working for
OL,17,Flogistics firm Manfreight Ltd, and was
OL,18,Fgiven two fuel cards to fill up
OL,19,Fcompany vehicles.
