OL,6,FPolice tried to trace James, but could
OL,7,Fnot locate him at any of the addresses
OL,8,Flinked to him. However on 27 March
OL,9,F2023, he was caught and arrested.
OL,11,FIn interview, he admitted he had been
OL,12,Ffilling up fuel drums and barrels and
OL,13,Fusing false vehicle plates which did
OL,14,Fnot show up on the police national
OL,15,Fcomputer (PNC). He claimed a man
OL,16,Fcalled Chris offered to pay him for
OL,17,Fbarrels of fuel.
