OL,6,FHe said he was in a controlling
OL,7,Frelationship with a partner who kept
OL,8,Fdemanding money, however that has now
OL,9,Fcome to an end.
OL,11,FPreston Crown Court heard James, who
OL,12,Fwas 20 at the time of the frauds, has
OL,13,Fprevious convictions for making off
OL,14,Fwithout payment and failing to keep
OL,15,Frelevant records in accordance with
OL,16,Fthe Transport Act.
