OL,6,FRecorder Catherine Dean, sentencing,
OL,7,Fsaid: "I am told by the author of your
OL,8,Fpre-sentence report that you are
OL,9,Ftormented by your previous behaviour.
OL,10,FI bear in mind your age at the time
OL,11,Fand that you were only 20.
OL,13,F"You also co-operated at the earliest
OL,14,Fopportunity. You attended an interview
OL,15,Fvoluntarily and made full admissions."
OL,17,FJames now works as a recovery driver
OL,18,Fand has saved up #6,000 to begin to
OL,19,Frepay his former employer.
