OL,3,CEx-employee helped himself to #52,000
OL,4,Cworth of fuel on company account
OL,6,FHe said he was eager to repay the full
OL,7,Famount lost to the company. He pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to six counts of fraud by false
OL,9,Frepresentation relating to more than
OL,10,F120 bogus transactions with the fuel
OL,11,Fcards.
OL,13,FJames was sentenced to 16 months
OL,14,Fsuspended for 18 months with 25 days
OL,15,Frehabilitation activity requirements
OL,16,Fand 120 hours of unpaid work.
OL,18,FHe has also been ordered to pay
OL,19,F#52,310 compensation and #150 costs.
